manifest_analysis.title:
Clear text traffic is Enabled For App
[android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: The app intends to use cleartext network traffic, such as cleartext HTTP, FTP stacks, DownloadManager, and MediaPlayer. The default value for apps that target API level 27 or lower is "true". Apps that target API level 28 or higher default to "false". The key reason for avoiding cleartext traffic is the lack of confidentiality, authenticity, and protections against tampering; a network attacker can eavesdrop on transmitted data and also modify it without being detected.
manifest_analysis.name: Clear text traffic is Enabled For App [android:usesCleartextTraffic=true]

manifest_analysis.title:
Application Data can be Backed up
[android:allowBackup=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: This flag allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.
manifest_analysis.name: Application Data can be Backed up [android:allowBackup=true]

metadata.description: This App copies data to clipboard. Sensitive data should not be copied to clipboard as other applications can access it.
The App logs information. Sensitive information should never be logged.
metadata.cwe: CWE-532 Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File

metadata.description: App creates temp file. Sensitive information should never be written into a temp file.
App uses SQLite Database and execute raw SQL query. Untrusted user input in raw SQL queries can cause SQL Injection. Also sensitive information should be encrypted and written to the database.
metadata.cwe: CWE-89 Improper Neutralization of Special Elements used in an SQL Command ('SQL Injection')

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin
playstore_details.description:
Bitcoin is an online crypto system invented by Satoshi Nakamoto, who published the invention in 2008 and released it as free software.

Looking for an app to easily and quickly send and receive Bitcoin? The Bitcoin application has everything you need to get started, 
whether you're new to cryptocurrency or an expert, we've got you covered.

FEATURES
⁃ Military grade extended security settings.
⁃ Application protected by password with recovery and extended Secure pin.
⁃ Sending and receiving crypto by QR code or address.
⁃ Balance tracking and detailed history.
⁃ Based on blockchain, transparent and full of trust application.
⁃ Details of each history, the number of confirmations, witness, block height.
⁃ Live market updates.
⁃ No web service or cloud needed.
⁃ Less is more: No support for alt-coins or tokens. No unnecessary features.
⁃ Display of Bitcoin amount in BTC and Dollars.
⁃ When you're offline, you can still receive.
⁃ Safety: Supports SEGWIT format.

All transactions are managed via BITAPS:
https://www.bitaps.com

Use at your own risk!
